      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 148.853, relating to tourism development incentives,  to increase the time a seasonal tourism attraction project is required to be open to the public from 6 months to 9 months in order to qualify for an extension in the term of its incentive agreement."
